### DASHBOARD
### ============================================

### Métricas gerais do dashboard
GET http://localhost:3000/api/dashboard

### Métricas de projetos
GET http://localhost:3000/api/dashboard/projects

### Métricas de estoque
GET http://localhost:3000/api/dashboard/inventory
